description: `build_hangover_montage.py` creates a video montage from images and videos, synced to a chosen audio track. It processes images (portrait or landscape) by resizing, cropping, or adding a blurred background. Videos are either kept at their original length, sped up, or split into chunks. The final montage is adjusted to the audio's duration and saved as an `MP4` file. Key features include memory optimizations, random clip selection, and flexible media handling (images and videos in multiple formats).
